element.name: checkin
element.documentation: Checkin process includes passport verification,issuing boarding pass to the passengers and droping baggage.

element.name: Passport verification
element.documentation: Airline employees checks for the passport and flight ticket of the passengers.

element.name: Issuing boarding pass
element.documentation: Airline employees prints boarding pass to the passengers.

element.name: Provide Paasengers service
element.documentation: Airline employees provide some services like seat selection, change of reservation, meal selection etc.

element.name: checkin service by emplyees
element.documentation: Airline employees checks passport and flight ticket and issues boarding pass and also they provide services like change of reservations, meals, seat selection etc.

element.name: Baggage handelling
element.documentation: Passengers can drop their baggage at checkin counters and pay extra fees for excess baggage. Passengers receives tags to put foor cabin bags

element.name: Baggage Drop-off
element.documentation: Passengers hands over baggage whic is checked by the airport security.

element.name: Excess baggage charges
element.documentation: If the baggage exceeds weight limit, passengers are asked to pay surcharges.

element.name: oversized baggage
element.documentation: Weight of the bags exceeding from actual preffered weightage of the particular flight

element.name: Group checkin
element.documentation: Checkin process for the group of passengers

element.name: Change of reservations
element.documentation: Passenger reservation changes from or to business and economic classes

element.name: self service kiosks
element.documentation: Provide facilities for the passengers to checkin by entering flight boking details. It also offers facilities to drop the baggage , change in reservation of flight , seat selection etc.

element.name: Mobile checkin
element.documentation: check-in features like seat selection, meal selection etc can be accessed by keying in a website on the mobile phone's browser or by downloading a dedicated application.

element.name: checked bags fee
element.documentation: Extra charge to be paid for excess baggage.

element.name: Print baggage tags
element.documentation: Baggage tags will be printed inorder to tag passenger baggage for the identification of bags

element.name: Baggage tags
element.documentation: Tags given to checked bags/cabin bags as a proof

element.name: Airline administration support
element.documentation: Responsible in handelling check-in process and boarding process.
